First Storm
Why?
Why did my face get so hot?
Why did my heart beat so fast?
My face is hot.
How weird...
I am so pissed!
The boys in class 4 are slacking on the culture festival preparations
and ranking the first year girls in beauty!
They should look in the mirror, before talking.
Sounds like fun!
We should do a boys ranking too, Nanoka.
Na-no-ka!
Why are you so out of it?
Who is your top choice of the boys?
I do not really know the boys in the other classes.
How about Miyauchi?
I heard you went home with him the other day!
When did you get so close to him?
Yeah, when?
That is not it!
That day, we had to stay late to finish up some executive committee work!
The way you desperately defend yourself makes it even more suspicious.
That is not it!
Sorry.
It must be embarrassing for you.
Everyone... everyone is just kidding around.
Its fine.
I do not really mind.
Hey... would you read this later?
This?
It is something like a love letter.
But...
I just spoke to you for the first time the other day...
It is so sudden...
It is not from me.
It is from this guy named Asano in my class.
Oh...
It is... I see...
but it does not mean I dislike you, Miyauchi-kun.
How should I put this... umm...
Then, please take care of it.
Well he does not look like a bad guy.
I think he is nice, though he has a pretty plain face.
Hey, Nanoka, come here too!
Hey, let us stop spying on him.
So you say, but it actually bothers you, right?
Why do not you go talk to him?
He is probably just playing around with me.
I am sure that is not true.
Umm...
Why did you run away?
It was your chance to talk to him!
Yeah.
But there is always tomorrow.
You are going to look around the festival with him, right?
But...
Try going out with him for a day, and see if you want to go out with him for real after that.
But... but what... do you do when you'go out' with someone?
Well, there is a whole bunch of things!
Like walk home together, visit each others houses or walk through a park...
A park?
Maybe if you get a boyfriend you will be able to grow out of your brother complex.
I do not have a brother complex!
What is wrong?
Umm...
About tomorrow's culture festival...
I do not mind if you come too, brother...
Sorry, I have to work.
What is it?
You do not look happy.
That is not true.
Brother, you will not get mad?
He does not seem like a bad person, but the letter seems so easygoing...
I was thinking that maybe he is just making fun of me.
I should not go out with a boy I have never even talked to before, right?
I do not really know this boy very well...
So he is saying you should try hanging out with him.
Futaba-chan said the same thing.
Do not show me letters like this.
It may look like he is just being casual but he might be pretty serious.
Should you show such important letters so casually to a third person?
I just wanted to talk to someone about it
because I do not know what to do!
So, if he does not seem like a bad guy, try going out with him once.
So, if he does not seem like a bad guy, try going out with him once.
And if you think you guys would click, go out with him.
Maybe it will go well.
Is it okay?
Do not ask me such things...
But... you got really mad the other time when Miyauchi-kun just walked me home.
I am sorry about that.
I will not treat you like a kid anymore.
Do as you like.
I see.
I guess you are right.
It is my own problem.
I can decide on my own.
Thanks for listening to me.
That is right.
Besides... my brother... has nothing to do with it.
Umm...
I cannot really think about going out with anyone right now...
I was just thinking that it would be cool if we could hang out together, today.
But...
Is there someone else you like?
No... it is not like that!
Do not worry about it.
I do not really mind.
I am actually kind of busy with my class haunted house.
I have to go back now!
Looks like I have troubled you, sorry!
I am the one that has to apologize...
Do as you like.
Huh?
Weird...
That is weird...
A photo of my brother?
You do not have one?
He ended up not coming to the culture festival, so...
I want to see what kind of prince this brother you are always talking about looks like.
No.
He is not very good looking.
His beard is all bushy and he kind of smells like an old man.
He smells bad?
What does he smell like?
A weird smell?
Can you put this in the wash?
Eh?
Does it smell that bad?
It does not really stink, but...
The scores are 3 runs apart.
Bottom of the 9th with 2 outs.
Runners on 1st and 3rd base.
The batter is Yoshimura.
Today, he is 2 for 4.
If he hits a home run, the score will be tied but-
It is hit hard, down the first base line and... it is foul.
It had the distance, but it sliced right.
The closer, Ueda, is warming up in the bullpen...
but the manager, Oomori, shows no move.
2nd pitch, he hits it!
He hits a line drive straight into right field!
The runner on 3rd comes home.
Runner on 1st rounds 3rd and heads for home.
Brother...
Will you help me with my homework?
No.
It is too troublesome.
Why?
I forgot what I studied in high school.
Stop staring at me!
I was not staring.
You are making me lose my concentration.
All you have to do for that one is put it in the equation.
Oh... I knew that!
That is so not cute.
Then how about this one?
Look over it carefully.
At what?
You messed up on the first calculation for this one.
No way...
The homework was due today?
Nanoka!
You are so hopeless.
I will not make it on time!
The teacher's going to come!
If Futaba-chan and the others saw my brother... what would they say?
I wonder if my brother is handsome or not?
Later.
That is early!
Is your sister making a home made dinner for you?
Yeah.
He is now unperturbed even when I bring up his younger sister.
My brother always looks disgruntled, and I do not really know what goes on in his mind.
He is mean and grumpy,
and yet sometimes he is nice...
and it surprises me.
Idiot!
That is dangerous!
Sorry...
So umm..
How did it go with that guy who wrote you the letter?
Did you have fun at the culture festival?
If you have something on your mind, feel free to talk to me.
Oh... that...
Like, if you do not know how to go out with him or...
if you are having a hard time with things like that.
I turned him down.
Oh... you did?
Yeah.
What?
Did you worry about me?
Not really.
You were concerned about me?
No I said!
Besides, it is 10 years too early for you to be getting a guy.
You said you would not treat me like a kid any more.
What kind of adult would swing a bag around so much?
Were you following me the whole way?
Are you kidding me?
I just saw you on top of that hill and...
How sick!
You were looking at me secretly and laughing!
I was not laughing.
I think it is fine, something Nanoka would do.
You just called me Nanoka for the first time...
R-Really?
Yeah!
You always say hey you so condescendingly!
I am not really being condescending.
I am always the one that gets surprised...
It is unfair...
I do not know what you are saying.
I love you brother.
What are you saying!?
I did not mean it like that!
What do yo mean?
You are weird... blushing like that!
So weird!
I know...
I am going ahead!
What is she saying...?
